'''2016年尼斯袭击'''，是2016年7月14日在[[法國|法國]][[尼斯|尼斯]]的一場[[恐怖襲擊|恐怖襲擊]]事件。[[突尼斯|突尼斯]]裔法国人<ref>{{cite news|title=Attentat de Nice : ce que l'on sait du chauffeur, Mohamed Lahouaiej Bouhlel|url=http://tempsreel.nouvelobs.com/societe/attaque-de-nice/20160715.OBS4681/attentat-de-nice-ce-que-l-on-sait-du-chauffeur-du-camion.html|accessdate=2016-07-15|work=Nouvel Obs|language=fr|archive-date=2016-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716131816/http://tempsreel.nouvelobs.com/societe/attaque-de-nice/20160715.OBS4681/attentat-de-nice-ce-que-l-on-sait-du-chauffeur-du-camion.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>穆罕默德·拉豪杰·布哈勒蓄意驾驶一辆[[货车|货车]]撞向在法国[[尼斯|尼斯]][[盎格鲁街|盎格鲁街]]庆祝[[法國國慶日|國慶日]]的人群，隨後又向民眾開槍，造成至少86人喪生<ref name="startrib"/>。袭击者一边以Z字形驾驶货车向人群衝撞，一边高喊“[[真主至大|真主至大]]”<ref>{{cite web|title=Nice Terror Attack: Truck driver shouting Allahu Akbar kills 84 on Bastille Day|url=https://www.thesun.co.uk/news/1447619/at-least-77-dead-and-100-injured-as-lorry-crashes-into-crowd-of-revellers-celebrating-in-france-terror-attack/|website=The Sun|accessdate=2016-07-15|archive-date=2016-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715004215/https://www.thesun.co.uk/news/1447619/at-least-77-dead-and-100-injured-as-lorry-crashes-into-crowd-of-revellers-celebrating-in-france-terror-attack/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Boyle_2016-07-14_DailyMail">{{cite news|last1=Boyle|first1=Darren|last2=Tonkin|first2=Sam|date=14 July 2016|title=Gun and truck attack leaves at least 80 dead in Nice: Men, women and kids strewn across road after lorry speeds for a MILE through holiday crowd watching fireworks, before gunman opens fire|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3691019/Several-people-injured-truck-crashes-crowd-Bastille-Day-celebrations-Nice.html|newspaper=Daily Mail|access-date=2016-07-15|archive-date=2018-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180409222609/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3691019/Several-people-injured-truck-crashes-crowd-Bastille-Day-celebrations-Nice.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Henderson_2016-07-14_TheTelegraph">{{cite news |last1=Henderson |first1=Barney |last2=Graham |first2=Graham |date=2016-07-14 |title=Nice terror attack: 80 killed by truck crashing into Bastille Day crowd and ploughing into pedestrians for up to 2km then spraying them with bullets |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/07/14/truck-crashes-into-crowd-at-bastille-day-celebrations-in-nice2/ |newspaper=The Telegraph |access-date=2016-07-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160714232325/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/07/14/truck-crashes-into-crowd-at-bastille-day-celebrations-in-nice2/ |archivedate=2016-07-14 }}</ref>。最终他被警方击毙。这是自2015年1月7日的[[查理周刊总部枪击案|查理周刊总部枪击案]]和2015年11月13日的[[2015年11月巴黎袭击事件|2015年11月巴黎袭击事件]]之后法国发生的第三起較大型的恐怖袭击<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/16/world/europe/attack-nice-bastille-day.html|title=Death Toll From Terrorist Attack in Nice, France, Rises to 84|last=Breeden|first=Alissa J. Rubin, Adam Nossiter, Aurelien|date=2016-07-15|last2=Blaise|first2=Lilia|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=2016-07-15|archive-date=2016-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715192432/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/16/world/europe/attack-nice-bastille-day.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]於7月16日宣稱本次襲擊是其所為。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jul/16/islamic-state-claims-responsibility-for-nice-truck-attack |title=Nice truck attack: Islamic State claims responsibility |publisher=The Guardian |date=2016-07-16 |accessdate=2016-07-17 |archive-date=2017-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171111204926/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/jul/16/islamic-state-claims-responsibility-for-nice-truck-attack |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==背景==
[[File:La_Promenade_des_Anglais_(14668462882).jpg|thumb]][[盎格鲁街|盎格鲁街]]焰火表演]]
袭击当天上午，[[法国总统|法国总统]][[弗朗索瓦·奥朗德|弗朗索瓦·奥朗德]]重申[[2015年11月巴黎袭击事件|2015年11月巴黎袭击事件]]后实施的紧急状态将于2016年7月26日[[环法自行车赛|环法自行车赛]]后结束<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.france24.com/fr/20160714-hollande-fin-etat-durgence-ei-tour-france-26-juillet-terrorisme-attentats-13-novembre|title=Hollande confirms the end of a state of emergency after the Tour de France|accessdate=2016-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715142944/http://www.france24.com/fr/20160714-hollande-fin-etat-durgence-ei-tour-france-26-juillet-terrorisme-attentats-13-novembre|archive-date=2016-07-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。法国刚办完[[2016年欧洲足球锦标赛|2016年欧洲足球锦标赛]]，期间该国落实了广泛的措施，并部署了众多军人。事件接续了包括{{le|2014年第戎袭击|2014 Dijon attack}}和{{le|2014年南特袭击|2014 Nantes attcak}}在内的一连串针对平民的[[車輛衝撞攻擊|驾车袭击]]，[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]和[[基地组织|基地组织]]都鼓励生活在西方国家的同情者实施这样的袭击<ref name="BergenTruckAttacks">{{cite news|last1=Bergen|first1=Peter|title=Truck attacks -- a frightening tool of terror, with a history|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/14/opinions/truck-attacks-tactic-analysis-bergen/|accessdate=2016-07-15|publisher=CNN|date=2016-07-15|archive-date=2016-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716123844/http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/14/opinions/truck-attacks-tactic-analysis-bergen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在尼斯，7月14日晚，数千人会在海滨大街欣赏[[焰火|焰火]]，庆祝国庆日<ref>{{cite news | last=Higgins | first=Andrew | title=In Nice, a Vibrant Celebration Gives Way to a Trail of Death | work=The New York Times | date=2016-07-14 | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/15/world/europe/nice-bastille-day.html | accessdate=2016-07-15 | archive-date=2016-07-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716064651/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/15/world/europe/nice-bastille-day.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=BBCNewsUpdate/>。
