==過程==
[[File:Negresco_de_nuit.jpg|thumb]]后来被用作医院]]
[[欧洲中部夏季时间|当地时间]]22时10分许，即事发前30分钟，一辆白色大货车被看见驶近盎格鲁海滨大道，开车不正常。之后货车转向海滨大道，冲向朝西南方冲过去<ref name=BBCNewsUpdate/>。

[[煙火|煙火]]表演刚在当地时间22点40分结束时<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.jpost.com/International/Dozens-dead-as-truck-plows-into-crowd-in-Nice-France-on-Bastille-Day-460465|title=At least 74 killed as truck plows into crowd in Nice, France, on Bastille Day|work=The Jerusalem Post|accessdate=2016-07-15|archive-date=2016-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160717182728/http://www.jpost.com/International/Dozens-dead-as-truck-plows-into-crowd-in-Nice-France-on-Bastille-Day-460465|dead-url=no}}</ref>，货车撞坏伦瓦尔（{{lang|fr|Lenval}}）儿童医院对面的路障<ref name=BBCNewsUpdate/>。一名摩托车手试着超过货车<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/07/15/hero-motorcyclist-attempted-to-stop-nice-terror-attacker/ | title=Hero motorcyclist attempted to stop Nice terror attacker | work=The Telegraph | date=2016-07-15 | accessdate=2016-07-16 | last1=Willgress | first1=Lydia | first2=Henry | last2=Samuel | archive-date=2016-07-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715160559/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/07/15/hero-motorcyclist-attempted-to-stop-nice-terror-attacker/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>，并打开驾驶员一侧的车门，但倒在了货车车轮底下。附近两位警察目睹这一幕随即向货车开枪。此时，司机加速，驶向东北方，猛冲向长廊的人群，突然转向撞到行人。警方尝试开枪阻止他，司机向警方和人流开火还击。货车继续行驶两公里，撞死或弄伤行人。目击者{{le|埃里克·塔蒂|Éric Ciotti}}表示，有人曾跳向货车，分散并吸引司机的火力<ref name=NYTimes>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/live/truck-plows-into-crowd-in-nice-france/how-the-truck-was-stopped/ |title=How the Truck Was Stopped |work=The New York Times |date=2016-07-15 |accessdate=2016-07-15 |archive-date=2016-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160716131815/http://www.nytimes.com/live/truck-plows-into-crowd-in-nice-france/how-the-truck-was-stopped/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同时警方在[[地中海宫|地中海宫]]酒店附近包围车辆<ref name=BBCNewsUpdate>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36801671 |title=Nice attack: What we know of the Bastille Day killings |publisher=BBC |date=2016-07-15 |accessdate=2016-07-15 |archive-date=2019-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502203658/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36801671 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。车子最终被枪火扫射，司机被毙<ref name=BBCNewsUpdate/><ref name="cnn_20160714">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/14/europe/nice-truck-attack-live-blog/index.html|title=Live updates: Truck driver attacks crowd in Nice, killing dozens|first=Steve|last=Almasy|date=2016-07-14|work=CNN|accessdate=2016-07-15|archive-date=2016-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160717134121/http://www.cnn.com/2016/07/14/europe/nice-truck-attack-live-blog/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

警方在货车上搜获一枚[[弹匣|弹匣]]、一枚手榴弹、翻版{{le|卡拉什尼科夫步枪|Kalashnikov rifle}}和[[M16步枪|M16步枪]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36808020 |title=Lorry have guns inside |work=BBC |date=2016-07-15 |access-date=2016-07-15 |archive-date=2016-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715192835/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36808020 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==兇徒==
{{main|穆罕默德·拉胡瓦杰·布哈勒}}

[[File:Lahouaiej_Bouhlel.jpg|thumb]]照片。]]
法国媒体认定嫌犯为31岁的突尼斯籍男子[[穆罕默德·拉胡瓦杰·布哈勒|穆罕默德·拉胡瓦杰·布哈勒]]<ref name="Atlantico 15 July 2016">{{cite news|title=Attentat de Nice : ce que l'on sait du tueur du 14 juillet|url=http://www.atlantico.fr/pepites/attentat-nice-que-on-sait-tueur-14-juillet-2765127.html|date=2016-07-15|accessdate=2016-07-15|work=Atlantico|language=fr|archive-date=2018-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930121815/http://www.atlantico.fr/pepites/attentat-nice-que-on-sait-tueur-14-juillet-2765127.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，有尼斯的生活和永久居住权<ref name="auto1">{{cite news|url=http://www.europe1.fr/faits-divers/attentat-a-nice-ce-que-lon-sait-du-supect-2800117|publisher=Europe1|title=Attentat à Nice : le suspect a été formellement identifié|accessdate=15 July 2016|language=fr|archive-date=2019-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407203414/https://www.europe1.fr/faits-divers/attentat-a-nice-ce-que-lon-sait-du-supect-2800117|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据报道他有财务困难，曾当过司机，在袭击发生约一年前获得货车驾驶证<ref name="Atlantico 15 July 2016" />。作案的大貨車是他在事發前數天租用的。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/07-15/7940617.shtml |title=尼斯恐袭车辆在事发前数日已租好 |publisher=中新網 |date=2016-07-15 |accessdate=2016-07-16 |archive-date=2016-08-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818092851/http://www.chinanews.com/gj/2016/07-15/7940617.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>布哈勒的父母已离婚，住在法国<ref name="BBC"/>。据媒体报道，布哈勒因此前五次刑事犯罪，特别是持枪暴力行为被警方注意到<ref name="Payton 2016">{{cite news | title=Nice terror attack: Police arrest killer Mohamed Lahouaiej Bouhlel's wife | work=The Independent | date=2016-07-15 | url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/nice-terror-attack-police-arrest-killer-mohamed-lahouaiej-bouhlels-wife-a7139201.html | accessdate=2016-07-15 | last=Payton | first=Matt | archive-date=2016-07-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715192113/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/nice-terror-attack-police-arrest-killer-mohamed-lahouaiej-bouhlels-wife-a7139201.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。他于事发约一个月前因疲劳驾驶引发交通事故被捕，案发时仍受司法监督。然而他没有被法国当局认定为国家安全威胁（{{le|S卡|fiche "S"}}）<ref name="Atlantico 15 July 2016" />。

目击者曾表示布哈勒在袭击期间曾高喊“[[大赞辞|真主至大]]”，但这些报告<ref name="Henderson_2016-07-14_TheTelegraph"/>未被官员证实<ref name="rumors">{{cite news|title=Nice lorry attack sparks false rumours on social media|access-date=2016-07-15|date=2016-07-15|publisher=BBC News|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36807333|first=Rozina|last=Sini|archive-date=2018-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930122025/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36807333|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据他的邻居表示，他没有去过清真寺祈祷，对宗教并不十分感兴趣<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/07/15/who-is-the-nice-terror-attacker-everything-we-know-so-far/ | title=Who is the Nice terror attack suspect? Everything we know so far about Mohamed Lahouaiej Bouhlel | date=2016-07-16 | accessdate=2016-07-16 | archive-date=2016-07-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715190233/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/07/15/who-is-the-nice-terror-attacker-everything-we-know-so-far/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。布哈勒妻子的表兄也证实这一点<ref name="Payton 2016" />。

突尼斯當局未發現他在突尼斯境内参与任何恐怖主义活动<ref name="BBC"/>。然而，他因与跟毒品和接近酒精相关罪行有关系而被当局注意<ref name="Atlantico 15 July 2016" />。法国检察官表示，袭击“承载着[[伊斯兰恐怖主义|圣战恐怖主义]]的标志”，但没有组织声称对袭击负责<ref name="BBC"/>，法国官员初步调查表明布哈勒跟任何国际恐怖组织都没有联系<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.buzzfeed.com/tasneemnashrulla/heres-what-we-know-about-the-suspect-in-the-nice-attack|title=Here's What We Know About The Suspect in the Nice Attack|work=BuzzFeed|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2017-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170706130515/https://www.buzzfeed.com/tasneemnashrulla/heres-what-we-know-about-the-suspect-in-the-nice-attack|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[法国总理|法国总理]][[曼努埃尔·瓦尔斯|曼努埃尔·瓦尔斯]]表示，嫌犯“很可能跟伊斯兰教激进派有着联系”，在法国国内外打击恐怖主义和伊斯兰教激进派的“战争”背景下策动袭击<ref>{{Cite news|title=France's Valls says Nice attacker linked 'one way or another' to radical Islam|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/us-europe-attacks-nice-valls-idUSKCN0ZV2CR?il=0|agency=Reuters|date=2016-07-15|accessdate=2016-07-16|archive-date=2018-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180930121826/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-europe-attacks-nice-valls-idUSKCN0ZV2CR?il=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这种说法立刻被法国内政部长[[贝尔纳·卡泽纳夫|贝尔纳·卡泽纳夫]]驳回，表示“我们有个没有因跟伊斯兰教激进派有活动而被情报部门注意的个人”，谁也不能确认袭击者的动机跟伊斯兰圣战有关联<ref name="BBC"/>。

布哈勒有犯轻罪的历史，但跟最近在法国策动袭击的恐怖组织或极端武装分子不同<ref name="rubin">{{Cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/16/world/europe/attack-nice-bastille-day.html|title=Death Toll From Terrorist Attack in Nice, France, Rises to 84|last=Breeden|first=Alissa J. Rubin, Adam Nossiter, Aurelien|date=15 July 2016|last2=Blaise|first2=Lilia|newspaper=The New York Times|issn=0362-4331|access-date=15 July 2016|archive-date=2016-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160715192432/http://www.nytimes.com/2016/07/16/world/europe/attack-nice-bastille-day.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，屬於孤狼罪犯，然而犯罪防治學家指出，在[[法國|法國]]本地受到歧視的移民與第二代，因為文化排斥而融入困難，很容易被極端宗教思想所擄獲、煽動，特別是傳聲能力強大的[[伊斯蘭國|伊斯蘭國]]就宣稱過鼓勵在歐洲的穆斯林發動「個人聖戰」，必然相當可能以單方面的宣傳與此類潛在攻擊者搭上關係。

另一方面，有官員懷疑布哈勒在發動恐襲前實行[[塔基亞|塔基亞]]隱瞞宗教信仰，以避免成為執法當局注意對象。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.breitbart.com/london/2016/07/28/jihadists-may-leading-secular-lifestyle-stay-radar/ |title=Jihadist Killers Drink, Party, Lead 'Western' Lifestyles As Disguise Before Attacks |work=www.breitbart.com |date=2016-07-28 |accessdate=2016-08-01 |archive-date=2016-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160801110738/http://www.breitbart.com/london/2016/07/28/jihadists-may-leading-secular-lifestyle-stay-radar/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

